FEES/LICENSES/PERMITS. Provides relative to occupational licenses. (8/1/26)
1 AN ACT
2 To enact R.S. 37:23.5, relative to occupational licenses; to provide for judicial review of
3 statutory requirements for an occupational license; to provide for terms, conditions,
4 and procedures; and to provide for related matters.
5 Be it enacted by the Legislature of Louisiana:
6 Section 1. R.S. 37:23.5 is hereby enacted to read as follows:
7 §23.5. Judicial review of a statutory requirement for an occupation license
8 A petition may be filed in a court of competent jurisdiction to request
9 judicial review of a statutory requirement for an occupational license to
10 determine whether the statutory requirement burdens entry into a profession,
11 trade, or occupation and whether the statutory requirement is necessary and
12 narrowly tailored to fulfill legitimate fiduciary, public health, safety, or welfare
13 objectives.
