DIGEST
SB 266 Original 2026 Regular Session Pressly
Proposed law provides a petition may be filed requesting judicial review of a statutory
requirement for an occupational license to determine whether the statutory requirement
burdens entry into a profession, trade, or occupation and whether the statutory requirement
is necessary and narrowly tailored to fulfill legitimate fiduciary, public health, safety, or
welfare objectives.
Effective August 1, 2026.
(Adds R.S. 37:23.5)
